data.description: 45 acres. 360 degree views. 6934 sf of living space. Let us introduce you to Windsong Lodge, a stunning home 17 minutes from downtown Salida. Don't expect just a home when you tour this property. It is a lifestyle. The owners designed it for entertainment, abundant love, and laughter. They would often have 18 people at a time in the home, with some snowboarding down the front yard, others walking to three mile creek on the property and still others on one of the many decks enjoying one of the extraordinary views. On the inside, enjoy your high end appliances, hickory cabinets, in floor heat, and custom mantle above the fireplace. Want to be 30 minutes from downhill Skiing? 15 minutes from Salida's golf course? 10 minutes from gold rated fly fishing? Just minutes from some of the best hiking in Colorado, including 14,000 foot peaks? If so, welcome home. Seller is offering credit at closing for new carpet in the amount of $30,000.
